GOODBYE
MR. PLANKTON

35
00:04:40,989 --> 00:04:42,907
That jerk abandoned me.

36
00:04:42,991 --> 00:04:45,952
Tearing him into pieces
wouldn't be punishment enough.

37
00:04:46,035 --> 00:04:48,413
So why am I so worried about him?

38
00:04:49,497 --> 00:04:50,373
Damn it.

39
00:04:50,873 --> 00:04:53,543
What if he passes out at the wheel again

40
00:04:54,252 --> 00:04:56,212
and crashes?

41
00:04:58,923 --> 00:05:02,260
