Thank God!

45
00:05:13,896 --> 00:05:15,189
Where are you right now?

46
00:05:15,273 --> 00:05:19,819
I've been walking up this mountain road,
but it seems to be leading nowhere.

47
00:05:19,902 --> 00:05:22,071
Wait, more importantly,

48
00:05:22,780 --> 00:05:23,990
where's Hae Jo?

49
00:05:25,116 --> 00:05:26,159
Listen, Jae-mi.

50
00:05:26,659 --> 00:05:29,662
I’ll send a cab to your location.

51
00:05:29,746 --> 00:05:31,247
Take it and come to Seoul.

52
00:05:31,331 --> 00:05:33,583
Share your location with me.

53
00:05:33,666 --> 00:05:35,293
He's heading back to Seoul?

54
00:05:40,548 --> 00:05:43,134
Ma'am. She's on her way from Hongcheon.

55
00:05:43,217 --> 00:05:46,179
