I imagined what it'd be like to die.

789
01:10:38,943 --> 01:10:42,071
Hae Jo!

790
01:10:45,574 --> 01:10:47,034
Hae Jo!

791
01:10:48,953 --> 01:10:49,828
Hae Jo!

792
01:10:49,912 --> 01:10:54,583
Would it feel exhilarating,
like jumping over a high hurdle?

793
01:10:55,793 --> 01:10:57,002
Hae Jo!

794
01:10:58,337 --> 01:11:03,634
Or would it feel liberating,
like throwing off soaking wet clothes?

795
01:11:08,597 --> 01:11:11,892
