like walking from one subway car

796
01:11:12,393 --> 01:11:14,019
to the next.

797
01:11:17,439 --> 01:11:18,732
Hae Jo, no!

798
01:11:19,400 --> 01:11:21,485
No, Hae Jo!

799
01:11:22,111 --> 01:11:23,112
Hae Jo!

800
01:11:26,156 --> 01:11:28,325
You fucking bastard!

801
01:11:32,288 --> 01:11:35,374
No. That's not it.

802
01:11:38,085 --> 01:11:41,630
Now that I'm facing it,
it's nothing like that at all.

803
01:11:45,759 --> 01:11:47,261
I want to live.

804
01:11:48,470 --> 01:11:49,722
I'll kill you!

805
01:11:50,264 --> 01:11:52,224
If you die, I'll kill you myself!

806
01:11:53,475 --> 01:11:55,394
I swear I’ll kill you!

807
01:11:56,729 --> 01:11:58,147
No…

808
01:12:01,358 --> 01:12:02,276
I…

809
01:12:03,485 --> 01:12:04,486
I want…

810
01:12:07,698 --> 01:12:08,824
I want…

811
01:12:13,412 --> 01:12:15,539
I want to live.

812
01:12:21,462 --> 01:12:22,796
I want you in my arms.

813
01:12:29,678 --> 01:12:30,846
I want to love you…

814
01:12:32,848 --> 01:12:33,766
more…

815
01:12:36,185 --> 01:12:37,644
for longer.

816
01:12:56,038 --> 01:13:00,000
Hae Jo, wake up!

817
01:13:00,584 --> 01:13:03,462
Please, Hae Jo.

818
01:13:03,545 --> 01:13:06,840
Hae Jo, wake up! Hae Jo, please.

819
01:13:07,633 --> 01:13:11,303
Hae Jo, look at me. Hae Jo.

820
01:13:43,460 --> 01:13:45,587
In the end, the final scene of my life

821
01:13:47,256 --> 01:13:48,090
is you.

822
01:13:50,968 --> 01:13:54,054
Well I guess that means

823
01:13:54,805 --> 01:13:56,557
I had a pretty good life.

824
01:13:59,643 --> 01:14:01,687
Honestly, it was so much fun.

825
01:14:03,105 --> 01:14:05,357
In every way possible.

